methods.getNext:
Get the next node after the input node.

:param node: (IntrusiveSinglyLinkedQueue.Adapter.NODE_TYPE) - The input node
:return: (IntrusiveSinglyLinkedQueue.Adapter.NODE_TYPE) The input node's next node
methods.setNext:
Set the input node's next node.

:param node: (IntrusiveSinglyLinkedQueue.Adapter.NODE_TYPE) - The input node
:param other: (IntrusiveSinglyLinkedQueue.Adapter.NODE_TYPE) - The input node's new next node

text: Adapter interface for nodes with intrusively-stored next nodes.
